| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| **Focus** | Food and agricultural sciences, including geospatial applications in precision agriculture |
| **2026 Deadline** | ❌ Predoctoral: April 16, 2026 (closed); Postdoctoral: April 30, 2026 (closing today!) |
| **Next Cycle** | Expected ~March 2027 |
| **Website** | [nifa.usda.gov/grants/programs/afri-education-workforce-development](https://www.nifa.usda.gov/grants/programs/afri-education-workforce-development) |

