- [ ] **Submit AAG grants/awards applications** (November 15 deadline)
- [ ] **Apply to Commonwealth Scholarships** (opens September)
- [ ] **Submit Chevening application** (~November deadline)
- [ ] **Begin formal Fall 2027 applications** at target universities

### 🔵 WINTER 2026-2027 (December–February)
